name: Territorial Pissings
wikiSummary: Nevermind's most punk rock swipe, recorded in one frenetic take and played - against Butch Vig's wishes - straight into the mixing desk.  Also features Krist Novoselic singing a snatch of The Youngblood's 1967 US hippy hit 'Get Together' during the intro.  "Maybe some baby boomers will hear that and wonder what happened to those ideas", he mused.
wikiText:
Nevermind's most punk rock swipe, recorded in one frenetic take and played - against Butch Vig's wishes - straight into the mixing desk.  Also features Krist Novoselic singing a snatch of The Youngblood's 1967 US hippy hit 'Get Together' during the intro.  "Maybe some baby boomers will hear that and wonder what happened to those ideas", he mused.
